<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="discover-vt">discover <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'skʌvə(r)/    美 /dɪ'skʌvər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>发现；找到；发觉；了解到；查明：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Did you know when Columbus discovered the New World?
你知道哥伦布何时发现新大陆的吗？</p><footer>2017 江苏改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>discover + that / wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I've discovered that if I believe in what I'm doing and work hard at achieving my goal, I will succeed.
我发现，如果我相信我正在做的事并为实现目标而努力，我就会成功。</p><footer>2009 全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You'll discover what interests you by taking courses in many subjects.
通过学习多门科目的课程，你会发现你的兴趣所在。</p><footer>2009 四川</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>discover sb / sth doing sth：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They discovered him stealing money from others. 
他们发现他偷别人的钱。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We discovered him to be a good cook. 
我们发现他很会做饭。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>discoverer /dɪ'skʌvərə(r)/ n   </p></div>